Duplantis has a leap, it's a kick in the ass, laments the Swede's challenger
The 22-year-old American pole vaulter has the ambition and potential to be one of the new ruler's most serious competitors.
He already knows what it's like to beat Duplantis, two years his junior, having beaten him at an NCAA college meeting last year.
